cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CY 

This paper discusses the incorporation of linguistic, world, and common sense knowledge into AI/NLP systems, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the use of NLP methods to help construct and enrich lexical resources, which is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of lexical resources to improve NLP applications, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and cybernetics (cs.CY).
